MegaPirateNG Firmware
- 8 Input Channels
  - Throttle                / A8
  - Rudder                  / A11
  - Aileron                 / A9
  - Elevator                / A10
    - AUX1 - Flaps          / A12
    - AUX2 - Retracts       / A13
    - AUX3 - Nav Lights     / A14
    - AUX4 -                / A15
- 3 Servo Output Camera Gimbal
  - Cam Pitch / Roll / Trigger
- 4 Serial Ports
  - debug/BT/OSD/GPS/Telemetry Module
- 8 Analog Ports
  - Airspeed/Current/Voltage/LED Controller?
- 5V I2C
- ATMega 2500-16AU Microcontroller
- MPU-6050
- HMC-5883L
- MS5611-01BA03 Altimeter
- USB - UART
- On-board Logic Level Converter 

Flight Modes
- Acro
- Alt Hold
- Simple
- Loiter (GPS)
- Guided (GPS)
- Position (GPS)
- Circle (GPS)
- RTL (GPS)
- Auto (GPS) 
- Follow Me (GPS)

Weight 14.5g 

S0 / FTDI 
- Tx0, Rx0, 
- Can use BT, shared with USB, cannot be used at the same time

S1 - S3 
- Rx1, Tx1 for FrSky Telemetry
- Rx2, Tx2 for GPS
- Rx3, Tx3 for OSD



